{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "crm_management", "user": "michael_scott", "message": "Hey Julian, I've noticed that our CRM system is running a bit slow today. Are there any updates or maintenance going on that I should be aware of?", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "crm_management", "user": "julian_lee", "message": "Not that I'm aware of, Michael. I suggest you try restarting your system. If it persists, I'll get in touch with our IT team.", "created_at": 1620500200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "webinar", "channel": "webinar_participation", "user": "sarah_martin", "message": "Team, we have a new webinar planned for next week on the importance of virtual healthcare. Please review the content and provide your feedback.", "created_at": 1620500300000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "webinar", "channel": "webinar_participation", "user": "julian_lee", "message": "Sure Sarah, I'll run through it by tomorrow and provide my input.", "created_at": 1620500400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "crm_management", "user": "michael_scott", "message": "Thanks Julian, I'll give that a try.", "created_at": 1620500500000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "webinar", "channel": "webinar_participation", "user": "sarah_martin", "message": "Thanks Julian, looking forward to your feedback.", "created_at": 1620500600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "webinar", "channel": "webinar_participation", "user": "julian_lee", "message": "Team, I've been closely monitoring our customer engagement with the webinars, especially after our platform upgrades in December 2022. I've been tracking the rates for webinar invitations, and I've also segmented user lists based on their login frequency.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "webinar", "channel": "webinar_participation", "user": "julian_lee", "message": "This allows us to understand our active and non-active users better and tailor our approach accordingly. Additionally, we've introduced a gratification rewards system for attendees. This has brought about a significant change in our webinar participation rates.", "create_at": 1620500000002}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "webinar", "channel": "webinar_participation", "user": "julian_lee", "message": "I'm pleased to report that we've seen a 22% rise in webinar participation since these changes were implemented. This is a positive indicator that our efforts are helping to keep clients interested and engaged in our webinars post-upgrade.", "create_at": 1620500000004}}
